description: Deletes the cors configuration information set for the bucket. To use this operation, you must have permission to perform the s3:PutBucketCORS action. The bucket owner has this permission by default and can grant this permission to others. For information about cors, see Enabling Cross-Origin Resource Sharing in the Amazon S3 User Guide.

parameters.name: Bucket
parameters.description: Specifies the bucket whose cors configuration is being deleted.
